---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="About Lisa Tamati and PTL Signal.">
  <!-- Hero photo -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pt-16 pb-8 flex justify-center">
    <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-accent/40 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(0,212,170,0.15)] w-full max-w-sm">
      <img
        src="/lisa-tamati.jpg"
        alt="Lisa Tamati"
        class="w-full object-cover object-top"
        style="max-height: 480px;"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <span class="font-mono text-accent text-sm">// about</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2">About PTL Signal</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
      <!-- Bio -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-lg">
          Lisa Tamati has spent 25 years pushing the limits — first as one of the world's most decorated
          ultra-endurance athletes, competing in the planet's most brutal races across deserts, mountains,
          and frozen tundra. Then, when her mother suffered a catastrophic brain aneurysm, Lisa turned that
          same relentless drive toward cracking the code on human health and longevity.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-white font-semibold">
          Today she operates at the intersection of two sovereignty movements: health and wealth.
        </p>

        <p>
          As a functional health practitioner, Chief Science Officer and co-founder of longevity biotech
          <strong class="text-white">Aevum Labs</strong>, Lisa has spent over a decade helping people take
          radical ownership of their biology. Her podcast, <strong class="text-white">Pushing The Limits</strong>
          — 11 years running, over half a million downloads, globally top-ranked in functional medicine and
          longevity — has become a trusted resource for people who refuse to accept decline as inevitable.
        </p>

        <p>
          But Lisa's conviction runs deeper than biology. True self-sovereignty requires financial sovereignty.
          In a world being reshaped by artificial intelligence, Bitcoin, and macro economic upheaval, the people
          who understand these forces early will have options. The rest won't.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong class="text-white">PTL Signal</strong> is where those two worlds meet. Expect sharp analysis
          of AI, emerging tech, crypto, and macro trends — filtered through the same evidence-based, no-BS lens
          Lisa applies to health. Plus tools like the
          <a href="/earnings-analyzer" class="text-accent hover:underline">Financial Document Analyzer</a>, built to
          give independent investors the kind of intelligence previously reserved for hedge funds.
        </p>

        <p>
          Lisa is also the author of four bestselling books including <em>Relentless</em>, a sought-after
          international speaker, documentary filmmaker, and former television host based in New Zealand.
        </p>

        <p>
          Her full health and longevity work lives at
          <a href="https://lisatamati.com" target="_blank" class="text-accent hover:underline">lisatamati.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-navy-light border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-accent text-sm mb-4">// connect</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@LisaTamati" target="_blank"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-accent transition-colors">
              <span>YouTube</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://lisatamati.com" target="_blank"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-accent transition-colors">
              <span>lisatamati.com</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://shop.lisatamati.com" target="_blank"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-accent transition-colors">
              <span>Supplement Store</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-navy-light border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-accent text-sm mb-4">// topics</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {['AI', 'Crypto', 'Markets', 'Tech', 'Investing', 'DeFi', 'Earnings'].map(tag => (
              <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 bg-accent/10 text-accent rounded-full">{tag}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
